"Don't worry about that, I have a perfect way for you to spend time."
 He walked over to a data computer and pressed a button.  A CD ejected
out of a slot.  He walked over to an unused monitor and inserted the
disk into a drive just below it.  The screen lit up displaying:  Basic
Concepts of Grammar.

Two cartoonish looking bots walked onto the screen from both sides.
"Hey kids, today we will learn about grammar..." They continued into a
way too cheesy song about it.
